details.name: Vendetta
details.description: Allows Nyx Assassin to become invisible and gain a speed bonus.  If Nyx Assassin attacks to break the invisibility, massive bonus damage is dealt with the attack. Applies a break status on the enemy for 4 seconds.
details.upgrade_description: Grants new ability: Burrow. Nyx Assassin buries himself beneath the battlefield over a short duration.
